    public class BatchFilopodyan
extends FilopodyanGui
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    The main GUI and parameter store for Filopodyan. Extends FilopodyanGui to provide a GUI for running Filopodyan on a folder of images with pre-defined parameters.
    Author:
    Richard Butler
